data.description:
Easy maintainence... Windows fold in for easy cleaning, brick & vinyl exterior, treated deck is 720 sq. ft., a great place for entertaining! The i acre lot offers privacy and country quietness. Would be a good place to install a pool, garden pond, and fountain.
Neat split bedroom plan.
A cute cubby between living room and Master, makes a great little decorating area...could hold a curio cabinet, sofa table, maybe a mini office area.Cable ready and surround sound hook up in the living room.
The laundry room has a generator hook up and newly  added shelves and cabinets for storage.
This house is conveniently located close to I-10, giving you the luxury of country living and convenience to shopping and resturants.


Neighborhood Description

A country like setting with great neighbors &  near everything: Interstate, shopping centers, grocery stores, Post Office.
data.whatILove: We took up the carpet and had real hardwood floors installed in 2006. The floors are beautiful and easy care!
